Interface IModeTransition

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable

    public interface IModeTransition
extends IEntity, IIdentifiable
    IModeTransition: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This meta-class represents the ability to describe possible ModeTransitions in the context of a ModeDeclarationGroup.
